  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You've trained with the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-tomb-guardian.tomb-guardian.Item.5wago8PGRGfn9LdZ]{Sword of the Tomb Guardian}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-tomb-guardian.tomb-guardian.Item.tAcyAIL7c1goMGNO]{Tomb Guardian Glaive}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.2RrKSkj27NDREOKQ]{Gauntlet Buckler} your entire life. You gain access to these weapons, and have familiarity with them. For the purpose of proficiency, you treat them as a martial weapon.</p><p>You gain a 1st or 2nd level fighter feat.</p><p>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-tomb-guardian.tomb-guardian.Item.CJOEtUeHnEkoZ6Lr]{Scion Stance} action.</p><p>When taking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.Item.gApJtAdNb9ST4Ms9]{Fighter Weapon Mastery} and the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.Item.F5VenhIQMDkeGvmV]{Weapon Legend} class feature, you must choose either the Sword or Polearm group for each.</p>"
